          PAIR_TYPE (a:('a -> v -> bool)) (b:('b -> v -> bool)) x``,
    Cases \\ SIMP_TAC std_ss [pair_def,CONTAINER_def,FUN_EQ_THM]) |> GSYM |> SPEC_ALL
